summary: This document is an FBI evidence chain of custody form for an item seized on April 30, 2007, described as a red rope containing a book titled 'An Invitation to Poetry' and a Victoria's Secret white bra and panties set. The form tracks custody transfers of this evidence item, which is associated with case ID 31E-MM-108062.

events.title: Evidence Collection
events.description: A red rope containing a book and Victoria's Secret underwear set was collected as evidence.

keyFacts: Evidence item includes a book 'An Invitation to Poetry' and a Victoria's Secret white bra and panties set, collected on April 30, 2007.
The evidence is associated with FBI case ID 31E-MM-108062 and barcode E6516732.
The document is an official FBI evidence chain of custody form (FD-1087), indicating procedural handling of seized items.
